    "Transformers excel at handling extended sequences, making them ideal for text generation.",
    "Such DL models fall under the broader category of generative AI (GenAI).",
    "Natural Language Processing (NLP) refers to ML systems trained to understand and generate human language.",
    "When such a model is trained on a large set of text data, it is known as a Large Language Model (LLM) and it can generate",
    "text summaries and answer questions."
